Package: makaraValidatr
Title: Data validation tools for Makara passive acoustics monitoring database
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Jeff", "Walker", , "jeffrey.walker@noaa.gov", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for validating data in the Makara passive acoustics monitoring database.
    Includes functions for checking data types, ranges, and consistency. Designed for
    validating template files prior to submission to the Makara database.
